'''''Räsypokka''''' was a [[game show]] broadcast on the [[SubTV]] network in [[Finland]] from 2001 to 2003.  The show was hosted by [[Jaajo Linnonmaa]]. The title (literally "threads poker") stands for [[strip poker]] and sums up the content of the show, which often featured full-frontal nudity.  Two males and two females competed on each episode. Several episodes were filmed live at bars and dance clubs.

